# =============================================================================
# Affiliate / partner tracking URLs (optional until programs approve you)
# =============================================================================
#
# Workflow:
# 1. Leave these unset → the site uses safe public fallbacks (see lib/partner-links.ts).
# 2. When a company approves you, copy the FULL tracking URL from their dashboard
#    (often includes your partner ID in query params).
# 3. Paste into .env.local locally and into Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables
#    for production, then redeploy.
#
# Do not commit .env.local (it is gitignored). This file is the template only.
#
# Use HTTPS. http:// values are upgraded to https:// in code.

# Flights / flight search (e.g. Google Flights via network, airline program, OTA).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FLIGHTS_AFFILIATE_URL=https://...

# Hotels / stays (e.g. Booking.com affiliate link from Awin, CJ, or direct program).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_BOOKING_AFFILIATE_URL=https://www.booking.com/...

# Car rental (e.g. Rentalcars / network link).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CAR_RENTAL_AFFILIATE_URL=https://...

# Tours & activities
# NEXT_PUBLIC_VIATOR_AFFILIATE_URL=https://www.viator.com/...
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GETYOURGUIDE_AFFILIATE_URL=https://www.getyourguide.com/...

# =============================================================================
# Contact form (optional — uses Resend API; no extra npm package)
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. Create https://resend.com account → API Keys → RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
#
# 2. Testing before your domain is verified:
#    - Leave CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL unset (code uses onboarding@resend.dev).
#    - Set CONTACT_TO_EMAIL to the SAME email you used to sign up for Resend
#      (or another address Resend shows as allowed). Sending to random inboxes
#      (e.g. info@yourdomain) often fails until the domain is verified.
#
# 3. Production after domain verification in Resend:
#    CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL=Skyline Voyager <hello@yourdomain.com>
#    CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=info@yourdomain.com
#
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxx
# CONTACT_TO_EMAIL=you@example.com
# CONTACT_FROM_EMAIL=Skyline Voyager <hello@yourdomain.com>
